---
// 03-PricingTable.astro
---
<section class="w-full px-6 md:px-12 py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0A192F] to-[#050f1a] border-t border-[#5B0E1B]">
	<div class="text-center mb-12 font-spartan">
		<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-2 text-white uppercase">12개월 프리미엄 활성화 패스 수립함</h2>
		<p class="text-xs md:text-base text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">12 Months Premium Activation Pass.</p>
	</div>
	
	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-8 font-spartan">
		<!-- TIER 1 -->
		<div class="rounded-xl border border-white bg-[#071120]/90 p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03]">
			<div>
				<span class="text-[11px] font-black uppercase text-slate-400 tracking-widest">Basic Pass</span>
				<div class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-black text-white mt-2 mb-4">$19.99</div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-300">1개 구글 아이디 연동함. 1개 디바이스 등록 제한함.</p>
			</div>
			<button class="pay-redirect-btn w-full py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white hover:text-black border border-white text-white rounded text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider transition-all mt-8" data-amount="19.99" data-tier="Basic Pass">Activate Basic Plan</button>
		</div>

		<!-- TIER 2 -->
		<div class="rounded-xl border border-[#00FF66] bg-[#071120]/90 p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03]">
			<div>
				<span class="text-[11px] font-black uppercase text-slate-400 tracking-widest">Standard Pass</span>
				<div class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-black text-[#00FF66] mt-2 mb-4">$29.99</div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-300">1개 구글 아이디 연동함. 2개 디바이스 등록 제공함.</p>
			</div>
			<button class="pay-redirect-btn w-full py-3 bg-[#00FF66]/10 hover:bg-[#00FF66] hover:text-black border border-[#00FF66] text-[#00FF66] rounded text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider transition-all mt-8" data-amount="29.99" data-tier="Standard Pass">Activate Standard Plan</button>
		</div>

		<!-- TIER 3 -->
		<div class="rounded-xl border border-[#FF6B00] bg-[#071120]/90 p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03]">
			<div>
				<span class="text-[11px] font-black uppercase text-slate-400 tracking-widest">Pro Pass</span>
				<div class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-black text-[#FF6B00] mt-2 mb-4">$39.99</div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-300">1개 구글 아이디 연동함. 3개 디바이스 등록 제공함.</p>
			</div>
			<button class="pay-redirect-btn w-full py-3 bg-[#FF6B00]/10 hover:bg-[#FF6B00] hover:text-black border border-[#FF6B00] text-[#FF6B00] rounded text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider transition-all mt-8" data-amount="39.99" data-tier="Pro Pass">Activate Pro Plan</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
	document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
		document.querySelectorAll('.pay-redirect-btn').forEach(btn => {
			btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
				const price = btn.dataset.amount;
				const tier = encodeURIComponent(btn.dataset.tier);
				// 💡 대표님 주소창 인덱스 규격인 /02-payment 로 직격 전송 처리함
				window.location.href = `/02-payment?price=${price}&tier=${tier}`;
			});
		});
	});
</script>